trans-unit.source: Represents an ordered set of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.EmbeddedMailObject"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en ordnad uppsättning <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.EmbeddedMailObject"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: The EmbeddedMailObjectsCollection stores references to items that will be embedded in an e-mail message.
trans-unit.target: EmbeddedMailObjectsCollection lagrar referenser till objekt som ska bäddas in i ett e-postmeddelande.

trans-unit.source: The embedded items can be image files such as company logos.
trans-unit.target: Inbäddade objekt kan vara filer, till exempel logotyper.

trans-unit.source: The EmbeddedMailObjectsCollection is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MailDefinition.EmbeddedObjects%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MailDefinition> object.
trans-unit.target: EmbeddedMailObjectsCollection används av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MailDefinition.EmbeddedObjects%2A>egenskapen för den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MailDefinition>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MailDefinition> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MailDefinition.EmbeddedObjects%2A>

trans-unit.source: E-mail messages that allow embedded objects are configurable in the following Web controls by setting their <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MailDefinition> properties declaratively: - <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> - <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> - <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PasswordRecovery> > [!NOTE] > The values in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EmbeddedMailObject> and EmbeddedMailObjectsCollection objects are not stored in view state.
trans-unit.target: E-postmeddelanden som gör att inbäddade objekt kan konfigureras i följande webbkontroller genom att ange sina <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MailDefinition>Egenskaper deklarativt:- <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard>- <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>- <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PasswordRecovery>> [!NOTE] > värdena i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EmbeddedMailObject>och EmbeddedMailObjectsCollection objekt inte är lagras i vyn tillstånd.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.EmbeddedMailObject> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PasswordRecovery> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MailDefinition>

trans-unit.source: This protects against malicious users discovering path information for your server.
trans-unit.target: Detta skyddar mot skadliga användare som identifierar sökvägsinformation för servern.
